---

---

<div class="details-container">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <img
      src="/ceremonia.svg"
      alt=""
      class="section-heading-icon"
      aria-hidden="true"
    />
    <h2>Detalles del Evento</h2>
  </div>
  <p>Información útil para que disfrutes el día sin preocupaciones.</p>

  <div class="details-grid">
    <article class="detail-card">
      <h3>
        <img
          src="/vestuario.svg"
          alt=""
          class="detail-icon"
          aria-hidden="true"
        />
        <span>Dress code</span>
      </h3>
      <p>Formal — Color restringido: dorado</p>
    </article>

    <article class="detail-card">
      <h3>
        <img src="/carro.svg" alt="" class="detail-icon" aria-hidden="true" />
        <span>Estacionamiento</span>
      </h3>
      <p>
        El Club Táchira Tennis cuenta con estacionamiento disponible para los invitados.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .details-container {
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 0;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .details-container h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .section-heading {
    display: grid;
    justify-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .section-heading-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    animation: icon-float 4.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .details-container > p {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .details-grid {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .details-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .detail-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 1.2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .detail-card h3 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .detail-icon {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .detail-card p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @keyframes icon-float {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
  }
</style>
